  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Sepsis is a vital issue in critical care medicine, and early detection and intervention are&#xD;
      key to survival. We aimed to establish an early warning system for sepsis based on a data&#xD;
      integration platform that can be implemented in the ICU.&#xD;
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
